---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About · Nicolás Andrés Calvo" description="Cloud / DevOps engineer.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="about-head">
      <img class="avatar" src="/profile.jpg" width="120" height="120" alt="Nicolás Andrés Calvo" />
      <div>
        <h2 style="border:0;margin:0">Nicolás Andrés Calvo</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--fg-muted);margin:.3rem 0 0">Cloud / DevOps Engineer</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        I work on AWS, ECS Fargate, Terraform and Kubernetes, building infrastructure that is
        stateless, disposable and observable, and migrating the systems that aren't yet.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site collects case studies from real engagements: the context, the architecture, the
        decisions I made and what they cost. Names and figures in the public write-ups are
        generalized; the goal is to show how I reason, not to leak anyone's internals.
      </p>

      <h3>Certifications</h3>
      <p>
        My verified badges live on
        <a href="https://www.credly.com/users/nicolas-andres-calvo/badges" rel="me">Credly</a>.
      </p>

      <h3>Get in touch</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:nico.calvo2014@gmail.com">nico.calvo2014@gmail.com</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicolas-andres-calvo/">LinkedIn</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/NicolasAndresCalvo">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.credly.com/users/nicolas-andres-calvo/badges">Credly</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
